description: [``botocore``] Update lexv2-runtime client to latest version
[``botocore``] Update lexv2-models client to latest version

[``botocore``] Added new resource details objects to ASFF, including resources for WAF rate-based rules, EC2 VPC endpoints, ECR repositories, EKS clusters, X-Ray encryption, and OpenSearch domains. Added additional details for CloudFront distributions, CodeBuild projects, ELB V2 load balancers, and S3 buckets.
[``botocore``] AWS Elemental MediaConvert has added the ability to set account policies which control access restrictions for HTTP, HTTPS, and S3 content sources.
[``botocore``] This release removes a requirement for filters on SearchLocalGatewayRoutes operations.
